{"tid":166104,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不滿衣著被念　25歲孽子開賓士撞死父親逃逸","createTime":"2017-03-22T00:34:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-22T01:22:44.000Z","uid":36544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c0c5667b0641a08a6965d560bcc5d0deb4207059","tid":166104,"uid":36544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T00:34:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.ettoday.net/news/20170321/889143.htm?from=fb_gee\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20170321%2F889143.htm%3Ffrom%3Dfb_gee&d=JQdTOMZ4NvWA5L1F4kLiz10Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=b362a20c\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ettoday.net/news/20170321/889143.htm?from=fb_gee</a><br />\n<br />\n記者林煒傑／新北報導<br />\n<br />\n新北市汐止區一名25歲孫姓男子，19日下午開著黑色賓士載爸爸準備到基隆訪友，途中因為衣著穿搭遭碎念不夠正式，與爸爸爆發口角。行經大同路3段時，老爸憤怒要求下車，想不到孫少看著爸爸負氣離去的背影，竟引爆不滿情緒，直接加速衝撞，造成他全身多處撞傷，送醫急救後仍於當晚宣告不治。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2407/d2407733.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2407%2Fd2407733.jpg&h=ea9731c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n社會&nbsp;政治&nbsp;3C&nbsp;消費&nbsp;時尚&nbsp;大檸檬&nbsp;健康&nbsp;生活&nbsp;ET車雲&nbsp;房產&nbsp;親子&nbsp;旅遊&nbsp;寵物<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n和女神 相遇的一瞬間<br />\n<br />\n立刻安裝<br />\n<br />\nMeMe直播 - 華人線上Live主播電視及交友聊天平台<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n快訊／不滿衣著被念　25歲孽子開賓士撞死父親逃逸<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n2017年03月21日 17:43<br />\n<br />\n小&nbsp;中&nbsp;大<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n記者林煒傑／新北報導<br />\n<br />\n新北市汐止區一名25歲孫姓男子，19日下午開著黑色賓士載爸爸準備到基隆訪友，途中因為衣著穿搭遭碎念不夠正式，與爸爸爆發口角。行經大同路3段時，老爸憤怒要求下車，想不到孫少看著爸爸負氣離去的背影，竟引爆不滿情緒，直接加速衝撞，造成他全身多處撞傷，送醫急救後仍於當晚宣告不治。<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n▲25歲孫少因買衣服緣故和爸爸爆發口角，隨後竟開黑色賓士車直接將父親撞死。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，當天獲報原本以為是一般死亡車禍案，想不到車輛竟為死者66歲孫男所有，經調查才知道開車行兇的就是他的25歲兒子，而且孫少在肇事後，還直接開上貨櫃車引道往國道方向逃逸，毫無悔意，讓員警看了直搖頭，警方訊後將他依殺人、肇事逃逸等罪嫌移送法辦。<br />\n<br />\n▼衝擊力道之大，讓賓士車被撞出一個大洞。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2407/d2407732.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2407%2Fd2407732.jpg&h=263d315d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2407/d2407731.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2407%2Fd2407731.jpg&h=a8b236be&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aa8c47ff71c199340e98c9b47a86c01425cc890d","tid":166104,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T00:37:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35ea2c3dce9ea969d805a639cd4c4b50ae734ee5","tid":166104,"uid":41076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T00:42:33.000Z","msg":"乜撚嘢叫被念"},{"pid":"9dcc8cebcea372281c4f0305fe5b0ccab536cabc","tid":166104,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T00:46:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>乜撚嘢叫被念</blockquote><br />\n無睇hxh?"},{"pid":"566b5ecf9e83154539a8a2c442432cc040e843ba","tid":166104,"uid":36544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T00:46:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>乜撚嘢叫被念</blockquote><br />\n無睇hxh?</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdc5a0ffcbaf33e20d1210b136fc8062b54caa88","tid":166104,"uid":1675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T00:49:37.000Z","msg":"又係新北"},{"pid":"6b9142e5cb70f44a7c2cd33d777da64efa5ba28b","tid":166104,"uid":47966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T00:50:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>乜撚嘢叫被念</blockquote><br />\n無睇hxh?</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n圓!"},{"pid":"ced20d21c2e7e5f8f5e6c7769645d3f9c5e25